\section{Qubit coherent control via the optical Stark effect}
\label{SectionCoherentControl}


\subsection{Proposed control setup}

To illustrate the controllability of the Hamiltonian in Eq.\ \ref{HeffI}, we interpret the tunability of the indirect excitonic gap in terms of its effect on the temporal evolution of the Bloch vector associated to the state of the indirect-excitonic qubit. To this end, we recast Eq.\ \ref{HeffI} as follows,

